				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$M\approx 0.1$$\end{document}, and finding this value is a long-term wish in solar observations and laboratory experiments (Yamada etÂ al. 2004; Yan etÂ al. 1992; Yokoyama etÂ al. 2001).

